{"tid":1632830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[十八區開花] 今晚花朵要盛開，一定要有明確目標","createTime":"2019-10-06T23:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T03:02:02.000Z","uid":96148,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"390fdfefd524ce80417b0fe1e682708bb3e8af8a","tid":1632830,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:45:49.000Z","msg":"經過左尋晚之戰，大家都好迷惘<br />\n互相指責、推卸責任的post 又出返來，我自己都好迷失<br />\n除左10月4號晚的18區開花，大家有晒目標知道要快閃黨鐵、藍店、中資、垃圾議員辦事處外<br />\n5號同尋晚吹完雞，d人都唔知做乜<br />\n試過某地區group 有人話要裝修的都裝修晒，出來有咩目標先？<br />\n<br />\n而家好多人都覺得今晚係要18區，係要快閃，係樓星期二唔好馬照跑舞照跳<br />\n但係快閃做d咩？唔通動員咁多人唱國歌就完左？<br />\n<br />\n我提議每區都揾d有symbolic meaning 的建築物，例如沙田區有中聯辦，荃灣區有黨鐵車廠<br />\n呢d建築物的裝修，一係效果會影響埋星期二，一係就代表緊極權政府<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益，希望今晚開花，係盛開<br />\n<br />\n祝武運昌隆"},{"pid":"5ab5536632fac497bea938def25dc50ad12b2beb","tid":1632830,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:46:04.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"493d4064c3263f8db4f342614f8e5ca8fc4c2ca5","tid":1632830,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:46:14.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"7f7fe83780cd4392593e8cea3eb50cf4ad930fa7","tid":1632830,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:46:24.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"d3966e5dea1aec72b0723991e890a89ad4514718","tid":1632830,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:46:35.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"594e55a43bfd6f4b28d862faadd531bc417a53fb","tid":1632830,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:46:45.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"fa91a660b9d7169a407338625fa9a7fdf2c00271","tid":1632830,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:46:55.000Z","msg":"自推6/10"},{"pid":"07260435d94622b10ac0f9021c9f794d1c907369","tid":1632830,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:47:06.000Z","msg":"自推7/10"},{"pi